decks.notes: The deck focuses on generating a massive amount of mana through various fast mana rocks and artifacts like Moxen and Black Lotus, as well as utilizing cards like Paradoxical Outcome to draw a large number of cards and replay these artifacts for even more mana. This allows the deck to ultimately perform a powerful combo using cards like Thundertrap Trainer to win the game quickly through a powerful storm mechanism or other game-ending spells. The deck also includes disruptive elements like Force of Will and Spell Pierce to protect its combo.

This deck aims to utilize the Paradoxical Outcome combo to generate a large amount of mana and draw cards in order to set up a winning board state quickly. It includes cards like Moxes, Black Lotus, and Mana Vault to accelerate mana production, along with cantrips like Brainstorm and Gitaxian Probe to dig for key combo pieces. The deck also includes disruption in the form of Mental Misstep, Force of Will, and Chain of Vapor to protect the combo. Overall, the key goal is to efficiently assemble the combo pieces and win the game in a single explosive turn.
